[2026-07-05T15:09:26.613Z] [INFO] [stdout] The PlanControls component already has all four buttons with correct handlers. The core issue is in `cancelGeneration` in the hook — it doesn't update local `plan.status` to `'cancelled'`, so after cancellation the Resume button never appears because `needsResume` checks `plan.status === 'cancelled'`. It also leaves stale `currentProgress` and `generationState` visible.
