[2026-07-05T15:12:04.328Z] [INFO] [stdout] `PlanControls.tsx` already had all four buttons (Cancel, Resume, Retry Failed, Regenerate) with correct handlers wired to `useStudyPlan` actions. The issue was in `cancelGeneration` in `useStudyPlan.tsx:154` — it aborted the controller and set `isGenerating: false` but never updated the local `plan.status` to `'cancelled'`. Since the `needsResume` check reads `plan.status === 'cancelled'`, the Resume button never appeared after cancellation.
